data.description: Welcome to your future home! This beautifully maintained property not only offers 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2nd floor laundry, a spacious 2-car garage but also comes equipped with modern amenities for comfortable living. The modern kitchen is equipped with SS appliances, granite countertops, stylish back splash, undermount sink, sliding glass doors to a patio and a serving counter w/more storage.Roof 2022 & stay cool during the warmer months with a newer air conditioning system.Your family's safety is a priority as well. This home is equipped with an active radon mitigation system for peace of mind.
